{"tid":855983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周國賢嘅密封罩好適合形容近幾年面對香港嘅處境","createTime":"2018-10-10T10:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T12:01:56.000Z","uid":22560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de07a993133811a90af555843576a40574280db2","tid":855983,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:53:16.000Z","msg":"叫過我數百次我也未懂反應<br />\n摑了我數百下我也未叫暫停<br />\n從疲倦的冷眼 凝望世間無情<br />\n尋找不到氣力嘆一聲<br />\n<br />\n幾年前見到社會上有不公嘅事會唔開心<br />\n見到政府又做on9同過份嘢會嬲<br />\n會想出嚟示威 做返啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n但最近真係攰啦<br />\n面對接二連三嘅垃圾大白象工程出事、赤化事件等等<br />\n今日又話唔知拎幾多億去起個島<br />\n已經無力再關心<br />\n因為知道做咩都無用<br />\n唔想再面對嗰種無力感<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58210c07a96c333bc1cc24643bb3867ae239ec7b","tid":855983,"uid":72831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d14c5e192ce37c247f463ecb30a87cfc5c5538e","tid":855983,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:56:46.000Z","msg":"今生不回家-移民"},{"pid":"f1c49884e8fbb5a6fa98e9d033fc08a9d0989ad5","tid":855983,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a045c3c98738b234a211af32d8ccf9366e53fb5","tid":855983,"uid":141656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:30:00.000Z","msg":"在天之靈 適合啲"},{"pid":"01c2a8022b13103691b6a654609c268d2f4e14ea","tid":855983,"uid":28503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"麻木到一邊乾香檳一邊抽煙觀看地震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fd6fd3022ea4bd5793c611fb5d1dbfd6275a28","tid":855983,"uid":197253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy